<p>This pattern is for showcasing informative headlines, statistics, and other positive content with a full width background. Header and paragraph text is displayed along with a vector icon to add context to the headline. A navbox is included to act as a reference link for further reading.</p>

<h3>Rules for showcase banners</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Navboxes must be included on all banners.</li>
    <li>Icons used must be Font Awesome icons. See the <a href="../font-awesome/index.html">Font Awesome</a> pattern page for a full list of approved icons.</li>
    <li>If there is a user case to use other icons outwith the Font Awesome selection, the digital communications team must be consulted.</li>
    <li>Only the coloured backgrounds shown in the options can be used. Different colours must not be combined when using multiple banners.</li>
    <li>For rules on appropriate use of navboxes, please see the <a href="../navbox/index.html">navbox</a> pattern page.</li>
    <li>The headline character count must not exceed 100 characters.</li>
    <li>The paragraph character count must not exceed 500 characters.</li>
</ul>

